{"tid":1476154,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[PDX] PRODUCEX101 - X1(엑스원) 討論區 (12) 光復香港 時代革命 + Debut D-13","createTime":"2019-08-15T17:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T09:44:40.000Z","uid":269128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"77f873fa09fa860e5793323f024f926ca2e3a3ea","tid":1476154,"uid":269128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:11:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>歡迎來到LIHKG X1(엑스원) 討論區！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">* 參與討論前請先細閱P.1規則</span><br />\n<br />\n「光復香港 時代革命」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJWrMPW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJWrMPW.png&h=594371f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">2019/08/15 23:21 李垠尚 cr. 一個唔小心</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0zh24A5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0zh24A5.jpg&h=45476afa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pcb49n7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPcb49n7.jpg&h=1219aa7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G0mAwjS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG0mAwjS.jpg&h=d1f9cef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>X1</strong>（韓語：엑스원 X Won）是由Mnet選秀節目《PRODUCE X 101》的出道承諾，由最終決選出線的11名成員所組成，於2019年7月19日正式成立的韓國男子音樂組合，成員名單以投票方式決定；成員依排名為金曜漢、金宇碩、韓勝宇、宋亨俊、曹承衍、孫東杓、李翰潔、南道賢、車俊昊、姜敏熙、李垠尚。2019年整體以SWING娛樂旗下藝人身份出道（各自則有所屬的經紀公司），進行為期5年的限定活動，前2.5年為專屬合約，後2.5年可於原本公司進行活動。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">/ X1 LIHKG /</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">本區規則</span></strong></ins><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">1. 希望參與討論的您能保持理性，禁止對X1的11位成員作出人身攻擊之言論。<br />\n2. 互相尊重，避免引起不必要的爭吵。<br />\n3. 歡迎繼續討論其他在PRODUCEX101中落選的練習生。<br />\n4. 若不能接受其中一項規則，煩請按上一頁離開本區。<br />\n(其他後補)</div><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">官方SNS帳號</span></strong></ins></div><br />\nFancafe（官咖）: <a href=\"http://cafe.daum.net/X1official\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcafe.daum.net%2FX1official&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=80a21f11\" target=\"_blank\">http://cafe.daum.net/X1official</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/x1official101/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fx1official101%2F&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=e9e1eeb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/x1official101/</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/x1official101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fx1official101&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=b93dd5ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/x1official101</a><br />\nTwitter（X1 Members）: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/x1members\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fx1members&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=e0b31eae\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/x1members</a><br />\nYoutube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCboVqbN79qGtz45u_7L8hOA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCboVqbN79qGtz45u_7L8hOA&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=39a2855c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCboVqbN79qGtz45u_7L8hOA</a><br />\nVlive: <a href=\"https://channels.vlive.tv/B049DD/home\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchannels.vlive.tv%2FB049DD%2Fhome&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=df8c04a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://channels.vlive.tv/B049DD/home</a><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/x1official101/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r